
mozzio - Portable C device I/O benchmark
----------------------------------------


Feature list:

* test and report large-bock sequential and small-block random I/O speed

* support files as well as raw devices

* support multi-threaded concurrent I/O tests 


Wishlist:

* compile and run on any unix operating system

* be configurable to scale from slow hard disks to big fast SSD RAIDs

* run across multiple hosts

* auto-size the parameters

